# Local build env (committed — holds only the PUBLIC always-pass Turnstile TEST key,
# never a secret). Loaded by `pnpm dev` and `pnpm dev:full` (astro --mode development),
# NOT by production builds (`pnpm build` / `deploy` / `shots` / `audit`). This keeps the
# lead form working locally with the test key even after the real sitekey is set for
# production — see src/components/LeadForm.astro and stages/ship.md. Real secrets never
# go here; the Turnstile secret lives in .dev.vars (local) and `wrangler secret` (prod).
PUBLIC_TURNSTILE_SITEKEY="1x00000000000000000000AA"
